{"about_the_game":"<strong>Toddlers can be friends, or food.</strong> <br> <br>The humongous clown-demon Toodles has escaped from his poorly constructed cage, so foolish villagers summon the mighty Player to protect them. They're gonna regret that. <br><br>Gifted with the magical ability to throw stuff, the Player will use any resource available to defeat their bloated nemesis. Sacrifice villagers, <strong>transform and consume</strong> cute wildlife, do whatever it takes to survive until you have enough strength to bring down the clown.<br><br>Balls will be your primary tools, and can be used to <strong>craft allies to fight for you</strong>. You will need to build an army before taking on Toodles. For starters, try different balls on the toddlers. <br><br>This puzzle has many pieces that can be put together in different combinations. Experiment with transformations and through curiosity you can discover multiple strategies for victory.<br> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Evolve toddlers into mutant followers to fight teddy bears.<br></li><li>Protect your ugly baby army with layers of poop armor.<br></li><li>Encourage extra growth by feeding them licorice allsorts.<br></li><li>Twisters will randomly transform them, for good or bad.<br></li><li>Toddlers can also be converted into yummy food or milk.<br></li><li>Mice can be converted into stuffed animals to reduce fear.<br></li><li>Rubber ducks are raw material to make additional balls.<br></li><li>Knock off villager heads then upgrade them into guards.<br></li><li>Arm now-braver villagers with powerful plasma swords.<br></li><li>Capture flying unicorns and bats inside floating bubbles.<br></li><li>Reshape gummy bear corpses into strange new friends.<br></li><li>Hunt nightmares to upgrade your army into monsters.</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1530240/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1621710794","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_asse